usage: delay.py [-h] [--no-replace] filename delay

A handy script to introduce a (+/-) delay in a subtitle (SRT) file

positional arguments:
  filename      Enter the name of the Subtitle file to be used
  delay         Enter the delay to be introduced in ms

optional arguments:
  -h, --help    show this help message and exit
  --no-replace  Create a new Subtitle file instead of modifying the existing
                one
